    "title": "PAJATEN ERES DIVINO",
    "content": "<div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:180%;color:#ff6600;\"><strong>PAJATEN ERES DIVINO</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>Me bañe en el marañón</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>divise unas  palmeras,</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>la cuesta que me espera</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>entrar a tu corazón.</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>Cavilé por la misión</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>erizado es el camino,</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>llegar a su destino</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>de monte y quebrada</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>alli de madrugada</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>Pajaten eres divino.</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:130%;\"></span></strong> </div><div align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:130%;\">VAHEMA</span></strong></div><div align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:130%;\">ENERO 2004</span></strong></div><div align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:130%;\">SUCRE BOLIVIA.</span></strong></div>",
