    "title": "ES SEDUCCION PASAJERA",
    "content": "<div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:180%;color:#ff0000;\"><strong>ES SEDUCCION PASAJERA </strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>La belleza se termina</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>en un abrir y cerrar</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>poco a de durar</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>la hermosura femenina</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>entre nostalgias camina</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>el orgullo de ser mujer</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>su encanto del ayer </strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>es seduccion pasajera</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>la vejez no te espera</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>tienes que aprender. </strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>vahema santa maria</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong> 11 de julio 2009</strong></span></div><div align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:130%;color:#3333ff;\"><strong>       Sucre Bolivia</strong></span></div>",
